 According to the New York Times, the production costs of Beats headphones are those 

00:06:00.159 --> 00:06:07.400
 sold for as much as $ 250, are only about $ 14. The reason that Beats is seen 

00:06:07.400 --> 00:06:12.590
 as a big brand, is because of their marketing and brand image. From the start 

00:06:12.590 --> 00:06:18.419
 Beats spending a lot of money sponsoring famous people. All the most famous 

00:06:18.419 --> 00:06:23.039
 Athletes wore Beats during their interviews, so consumers started to think that 

00:06:23.039 --> 00:06:29.680
 these were fashionable, expensive headphones. The high price, solid, heavy materials; 

00:06:29.680 --> 00:06:35.689
 Robust packaging and approval from famous people raised expectations and probably have 

00:06:35.689 --> 00:06:52.220
 psychologically make the headphones sound better, just like with the medication. 

